Class Inscriber

  • java.lang.Object
    • Inscriber

  • class Inscriber
extends java.lang.Object
    Class Inscriber retains methods concerning to input information of consumer, item, order or quantity to "sql_dml.txt". Calling them is leading to prepare ready "Insert" of record in SQL language which can be use in oracle database to add new row to existing table. Writing will be add to the file only if process of creating new object of Consumer, Item, Order, Quantity was terminated successfully.
    Version:
    2.0 15.03.2018
    Author:
    Magdalena Wisniewska
